♫ <i>Hey, you're so cold. 陰険で凶悪な目つき</i> ♫

30
00:01:53,250 --> 00:01:57,310
♫ <i>見え透いた汚い本音</i> ♫

31
00:01:57,310 --> 00:02:00,580
♫ <i>Lie lie lie だんだん見えてくる</i> ♫

32
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:02,600
♫ <i>Standing up better watch</i> ♫

33
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,740
♫ <i>Gonna let you know</i> ♫

34
00:02:04,740 --> 00:02:08,800
♫ <i>You make me bad　卑怯な言葉で</i> ♫

35
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,370
♫ <i>I’m a piece of threat bet</i> ♫

36
00:02:10,370 --> 00:02:12,740
♫ <i>you can’t break it</i> ♫

37
00:02:12,740 --> 00:02:14,330
♫ <i>Try Try Try</i> ♫

38
